                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/144837601/d49b21c0ce26010e00b3258d62766797_9150041886156043630.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Wellspring of War-Lust",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ชนะโดยจำนวนตัวละครที่ถูกกำจัดต่ำกว่า 2 ตัว",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3601,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/144837601/d49b21c0ce26010e00b3258d62766797_9150041886156043630.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Wellspring of War-Lust",
